53:58.802 --> 54:01.304
Brothers are taking turns 
visiting the two groups 


54:01.303 --> 54:04.000
and supporting them 
in the field ministry.


54:05.520 --> 54:07.522
In the past, 
the main challenge 


54:07.522 --> 54:10.914
