thanks to increased translation efforts, 


54:13.983 --> 54:17.786
the number of publishers 
has increased dramatically. 


54:17.787 --> 54:22.809
As a result, a Rutoro congregation 
was formed in 2014. 


54:22.808 --> 54:27.596
Next, a remote translation office 
was established in 2015. 


54:27.597 --> 54:29.802
