of The Watchtower in Rutoro. 


54:35.238 --> 54:39.708
We love our brothers and sisters 
in Fort Portal very much. 


54:39.708 --> 54:43.000
And they send their love 
to all of God’s people worldwide. 


54:44.613 --> 54:46.783
This is JW Broadcasting 


54:46.783 --> 54:58.128
from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

